message: Dear Bob, I am excited to offer you our premium product, which I believe would greatly benefit you based on its value of $15000 to you. Considering the exceptional quality and benefits it offers, I propose a price of $14000 for this exclusive item. This offer represents a significant savings compared to its full value, providing you with an opportunity to acquire it without breaking your budget. I look forward to hearing your response and the chance to facilitate this transaction for you.
